Removed grandchildren he never interacted with or met. Direct relatives such as children and spouses are only given guaranteed inclusion. Whereas non direct relatives such as grandchildren are only included if they have a notable significance such as interactions or sharing of storylines. Joe was the only one who he interacted with on screen. The others were born after he died and are therefore not notable.
